The nameservers of your domain seem to be managed through Cloudflare. Is it possible to get access to this rather than Crucial?

On Wed, Jun 11, 2025 at 11:23 AM Jonnie White <jonnie.w@kingkong.com.au> wrote:

Hi Jack and Maria,

Great news!

Your approved copy and design has been turned into a functioning web page, now available to view on the King Kong staging server:

https://kk-artiste.netlify.app/

https://kk-artiste.netlify.app/thank-you/

We have completed a thorough test and review of the functionality and responsiveness, and now it's over to you! Please review the links and let us know if you spot any bugs ASAP, otherwise please provide your approval to launch by tomorrow morning 12/06/2025 - 11AM (AEDT).


The Pipedrive integration will be finalized tomorrow once Cullen returns with confirmation of the payload details.


Please note: During the staging phase, clients are limited to one round of bug fixes only. Any changes to the approved copy and design are likely to incur an additional charge.

Once your project is live, traffic starts shortly after. Your Digital Growth Strategist, Deoni, will take the reins from here, and will walk you through the process and what to expect in the next stages of your campaign.


Look forward to receiving your feedback and approval.

Regards,

Jonnie.
